title: Walker Hayes on What It Feels Like To Go Insanely Viral with “Fancy Like” + Bobby on the ‘Producer’s Dinner’  Last Night + Mailbag: Husband is Already Using Baby Name without Us Agreeing On It
itunes:title: Walker Hayes on What It Feels Like To Go Insanely Viral with “Fancy Like” + Bobby on the ‘Producer’s Dinner’  Last Night + Mailbag: Husband is Already Using Baby Name without Us Agreeing On It
description:
Walker Hayes stops by the studio to talk about the writing process of his song “Fancy Like”, what it felt like when it went viral and the coolest thing he’s about to do with his family because of it. Bobby recaps the producer’s dinner last night. Bobby opens up the mailbag from a listener who is expecting baby number 2. Her husband is already using the name "Wylder" as the name before they've decided on it together but she doesn't like it!
